(203, 14, 23, 'About us'),
(204, 15, 23, '<p>Bardar Bakery is located 20 km from Chisinau, in the heart of Bardar Village. We are in a picturesque area, known, among other things, for the beauty of the tulip fields and the magic of the water lily lake. A place with old rural traditions that inspires us to create wonderful artisanal products, especially \"Poale-n br&acirc;u\" pies.</p>\r\n<p>Thus, in the almost 20 years of bakery, we managed to combine traditional recipes with modern technology of preparation and storage of products.</p>\r\n<p>A good part of the production process is manual because this is the only way we can imprint the traditional shape and taste on our products.</p>'),
